# SciSim – Unity Physics Simulation

This is the source code and documentation for the SciSim Unity VR project.

## 🔗 Full Project Download

Due to Unity file size and GitHub limits, the complete Unity project (including Firebase and plugins) is hosted on Google Drive:

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SPN4C9fh5YVywkUtXUskIfyFZ-o77O1S/view

After downloading, open the project in Unity Hub.

---

## 🔧 Project Features

- VR-based simulations
- Planetary gravity
- Firebase support
- Real-time physics graphs

## 📁 Folder Structure

| Folder            | Description                     |
|-------------------|---------------------------------|
| `Assets/Scripts/` | Core Unity C# scripts           |
| `Assets/Scenes/`  | Main simulation scenes          |
| `README.md`       | This file                       |
